# radroots_runtime

This is the README for `radroots_runtime`, which provides runtime configuration
and service helpers for the `radroots` core libraries.

## Overview

 * config loaders, JSON file helpers, and structured runtime error types;
 * protected secret-file seal and open helpers built on the workspace security
   crates;
 * service bootstrap, shutdown signal, backoff, and tracing initialization
   utilities;
 * an optional CLI layer for configuration parsing and process startup.

